1. Ralph
   Repository: https://github.com/snarktank/ralph
   Author:     Ryan Carson / snarktank
   Used for:   The "Ralph" pattern -- an autonomous agent that monitors a
               project, identifies the highest-priority improvement, and
               implements it as a pull request while the developer is away.
               Agent Relay's core loop (analyze report, plan tasks, execute
               iteratively, open PR) derives from this pattern.
